name: Baby Fart Flyer
description: Did you know babies can fart hard enough to fly? Well it is true – when they eat burritos. Stay in the air as long as possible by using your Fart Power to get achievements prizes like Binkys, Blankys, and even a Teddy Bear! Choose from preset heads and bodies or use a custom head from an image URL! On the main menu use the UP ARROW to scroll through some heads from the 'net...
